### User Profile API

#### Create User Profile
```javascript
// POST /rest/v1/user_profiles
const { data, error } = await supabase
  .from('user_profiles')
  .insert({
    email: user.email,
    dj_name: 'DJ Example',
    full_name: 'John Doe',
    city: 'New York',
    genres: ['House', 'Techno'],
